    "Furthermore, NER algorithms are closely tied to their assigned tasks, lacking generalizable ability and thus making direct transfer to other tasks challenging.",
    "Additionally, extracted information tends to be intricate, heterogeneous, and diverse in the field of catalysis, leading to unsatisfied NER performance and reduced accuracy 12.",
